Roger Federer Reaches U.S. Open Quarterfinals, Defeating Juan Monaco

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-09-06T05:17:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/roger-federer-reaches-u-s-open-quarterfinals-defeating-juan-monaco.html
Five-time champion  Roger Federer 
defeated Juan Monaco of Argentina 6-1, 6-2, 6-0 early this
morning to reach the U.S. Open quarterfinals.  Federer, the third seed from  Switzerland , had 14 aces in
his win. His next opponent will be Jo-Wilfried Tsonga, the 11th
seed from  France .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  